---
import PrimaryCta from "./PrimaryCta.astro";
---

<style>
    .content-wrapper {
        max-width: var(--max-page-width);
        margin-inline: auto;
    }

    .items {
        display: flex;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 2rem;
    }

    .item {
        border: 1px solid #636569;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        flex-grow: 1;
        padding: 2rem 2rem;
    }

    .smol {
        @media (min-width: 800px) {
            flex-basis: 40%;
        }
    }

    h2 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    p {
        font-size: 1.125rem;
        margin-block: 1em;
        color: var(--secondary-color);
    }
</style>
<div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="items">
        <div class="item">
            <h2>Call for Proposals</h2>
            <div>
                <p>Whether you want to talk about decentralisation, encryption, Matrix internals, safety, sovereignty of digital communication, community, collaboration in the public sector, UX, or showcase your fun experiments, there is a track for you at Matrix Conf.</p>
                <p>We welcome proposals from individuals innovating around Matrix, organisations working with Matrix, and everyone contributing to digital sovereignty.</p>
                <p>We do not welcome marketing talks in the CfP, but have sponsorship opportunities to help promote your product.</p>
            </div>
            <PrimaryCta
                href="https://cfp.2026.matrix.org/matrix-conference-2026/cfp"
                flexBottom={true}
            >
            Submit Talk Proposals
            </PrimaryCta>
        </div>
        <div class="item smol">
            <h2>Join the Chat</h2>
            <p>Connect and exchange with other attendees and the organising team.</p>
            <PrimaryCta
                href="https://matrix.to/#/#events-wg:matrix.org"
                flexBottom={true}
            >
            #events-wg:matrix.org
            </PrimaryCta>
        </div>
        <div class="item smol">
            <h2>Become a Sponsor</h2>
            <p>Step into the spotlight and join us as a valued sponsor of The Matrix Conference 2026. Our updated sponsors brochure is coming in March.</p>
            <PrimaryCta
                href="mailto:conference@foundation.matrix.org"
                flexBottom={true}
            >
                Email us
            </PrimaryCta>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
